Helper scripts:

[*] mocf_lyrics.tg.pl - fetches lyrics and saves them to a file.

ExecCommand1 = "~/moc-lyrics.tg.pl -a %r -t %t -f %f"

[*] mocf_notify - displays notification and runs Last.fm submit script.

OnSongChange = "~/mocf_notify %a %t %r %d %f"

[*] mocf_simple.sh, mocf_submit_lastfm - Last.fm submit scripts. Need running lastfmsubmitd deamon:
http://www.red-bean.com/decklin/lastfmsubmitd/

OnSongChange = "~/mocf_submit_lastfm --artist %a --title %t --length %d --album %r"
OnSongChange = "~/mocf_simple.sh %a %t %d %r"

[*] mocf_play_rating.sh, ratings_find - plays all songs in a given directory with ratings in a specified range

Usage: ratings_find min [max] dir
ExecCommand5 = "~/.mocf/mocf_play_rating.sh 5 %d"
